mages/thumb/b/b9/%27%D7%9C%D7%97%D7%9C%D7%95%D7%97%D7%99%D7%AA%27_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C.jpg/41px-%27%D7%9C%D7%97%D7%9C%D7%95%D7%97%D7%99%D7%AA%27_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b9/%27%D7%9C%D7%97%D7%9C%D7%95%D7%97%D7%99%D7%AA%27_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C.jpg/54px-%27%D7%9C%D7%97%D7%9C%D7%95%D7%97%D7%99%D7%AA%27_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C.jpg 2x\" /></a></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414091941\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: [show‐toc]\nCPU time usage: 0.092 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.389 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 265/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7574/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 565/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/100\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3627/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.040/7 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5619712/52428800 bytes\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  287.375      1 -total\n 65.21%  187.409      3 תבנית:הערה\n 20.58%   59.152      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים\n  6.14%   17.631      1 תבנית:חודש_חשוון\n  5.97%   17.142      1 תבנית:להיום_יום\n  4.47%   12.856      1 תבנית:אינפו\n  4.03%   11.575      1 תבנית:לוח_שנה\n  4.00%   11.494      1 תבנית:לחלוחית\n  2.97%    8.539      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים/מרחב_שם\n  2.31%    6.652      1 תבנית:היום_יום/י&quot;ד_חשוון\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key chabadped_1-infopedia_:pcache:idhash:19539-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414091941 and revision id 827228. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>"
